{"tid":1223753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禮拜日遊行如果有狗扮示威者搞事點算","createTime":"2019-06-14T19:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:59:51.000Z","uid":145803,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"99a8e8838f93a977b008ebaba4f5749f7037d5a7","tid":1223753,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:11:52.000Z","msg":"依家連登主流都係話16號嘅遊行期間唔打算發生衝突<br />\n有咩事都等行完先<br />\n以免影響民意 或者搞到遊行嗰日啲一家大細<br />\n<br />\n但係啲狗咁興扮記者扮示威者<br />\n萬一便衣狗混入人堆喺遊行期間搞事<br />\n例如係主動掉磚 帶頭攻擊其他狗<br />\n咪會比到籍口狗清場<br />\n又比政府同cctvb話係遊行人士出手先<br />\n<br />\n有冇乜野方法應付同預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b8e252ffad287167d53d3d9f39a86bc726d6dc","tid":1223753,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:13:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04af116609c518d310d2f72518e6759b0a688292","tid":1223753,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:13:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f85ea9867098ca20444c0dfcc9cb93fe37e5620","tid":1223753,"uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:14:36.000Z","msg":"就算有30萬人都好多人<br />\n有人搞事實可以制止佢"},{"pid":"74a0286fcc7248943386c383c5b21c9a9910632c","tid":1223753,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:17:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"012170cbd987a2c55e7cc24be24b812bdc6ce95f","tid":1223753,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"[呼籲]發覺好多黑警del晒自己fb passing out啲相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1220059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1220059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"575c1dea0e8921720a5abdfab27e66edde8e4188","tid":1223753,"uid":61084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:21:25.000Z","msg":"前排啲義士要睇住，有咩事即刻掀低佢"},{"pid":"625f3be6adac05764d5f317db64bc74aa66f5e4d","tid":1223753,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid"